        public void recordUnmergedMetrics​(ServerHttpRequestStats stats)
        N.B.: We prefer treating the K/V sizes as non-mergeable, even though we could technically merge these lists into a bigger list, because doing so would trigger list resizes and copying, which is less efficient. Furthermore, there is no benefit from the merging since we still need to do one record call per item.
